    public class ListMonitorImpl
extends ItemFeatureEntryImpl
implements ListMonitor
    An implementation of the model object 'List Monitor'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Message
    • Message Attribute
    • Default Ack
    • Default Severity
    • Monitor Type
    • Demote Prefix
    • Entries
